100% Online Option

Could be Free with NextLevel Jobs

*Part-Time, In-State student

Short-Term Certificate

Known as a Certificate (CT)

9 – 27 Credit Hours

Certificates (CTs) are industry focused and designed for workforce preparation. Earned in as little as 6 months, CTs will be your fastest path to getting into the workforce.

Courses in CT programs also apply toward TCs, associate degrees, and transfer options.

Long-Term Certificate

Known as a Technical Certificate (TC)

30 – 40 Credit Hours

Technical Certificates (TCs), like CTs, are meant for workforce preparation but include further training — qualifying you for higher paying roles, in most cases, than CTs.

Courses in TC programs also apply toward associate degrees and transfer options.
